snippet.title: STRIDE - Gameplay Concept Trailer
snippet.description:
STRIDE is already out in Early Access!

▶️ Play on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1292040/STRIDE/
⏰ Wishlist on Oculus: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/rift/3137940179578220/

STRIDE is a story parkour action game in virtual reality. Battle enemies in the canopy of a  quarantined metropolis. Experience the feeling of vertigo as you stream between rooftops and flow across balconies in your effort to save the city.

🔹Discord: https://discord.gg/bASKMYt 
🔹Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/JoyWay/ 
🔹Twitter: https://twitter.com/joywayvr
🔹Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/joywayvr/

Joy Way Team 🤞
